Stackoverflow

Requirements

-> Any non-member(guest) can search and view questions.
-> Members should be able to post new questions.
-> Members should be able to add new an answer.
-> Members can add comment to any question or answer.
-> Member can upvote a question, answer or comment.
-> Member can flag a question, answer or comment, for serious problems or moderator attention.
-> Members will earn badges.
-> Members can vote to delete or close any question.
-> Moderators can close a question or undelete an already deleted question.
